com.documentum.fc.client.search

Interface IDfValueRangeAttrExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDfAttrExpression, IDfExpression

    public interface IDfValueRangeAttrExpression
extends IDfAttrExpression
    Defines a search expression that requires the attribute value to be greater than a minimum value and less than a maximum value (or equal).
    See Also:
    IDfQueryBuilder.getRootExpressionSet(), IDfExpressionSet.addValueRangeAttrExpression(String, int, int, boolean, boolean, String, String)
